kewarm''\n| Bill Rogers\n|\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''I Am... Gabriel''\n| Doc\n|\n|-\n|2013\n| ''Road to the Open''\n| Rob Gollant\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''Not Today''\n| Luke\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[Season of Miracles]]''\n| Coach\n|\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''Let the Lion Roar''\n| Hilary Bishop of Poitiers\n| Documentary\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''[[Smothered (film)|Smothered]]''\n| Player\n| Also director and writer\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''Runaway Hearts''\n| Chief Tate\n|\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[American Justice]]''\n| Sheriff Payden\n|\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''A Gift Of The Heart''\n| \n|Indiegogo campaign<ref name=\"indiegogo.com\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/2061300|title=A GIFT OF THE HEART MOTION PICTURE|website=Indiegogo.com|accessdate=November 7, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''4: Go''\n| Game Warden\n| Also director and writer\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''Alien Intrusion''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://alienintrusion.com/|title=Alien Intrusion: Unmasking a Deception|first=Super|last=User|website=Alienintrusion.com|accessdate=November 7, 2019}}</ref>\n| Narrator\n|\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Roe v. Wade (film)|Roe v. Wade]]''\n| [[Byron White]]\n| Filming\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''The Dragon Unleashed''\n| \n| Post-Production\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Christmas Cars]]''\n| Uncle Denver<ref>https://popculture.com/celebrity/2019/10/13/dukes-of-hazzard-john-schneider-drives-general-lee-again-christmas-cars-trailer/</ref>\n| \n|-\n| ????\n| ''Switched''\n| Ken Sharp\n|\n|}\n\n==Discography==\n\n===Albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n! colspan=\"3\"| Chart positions\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Label\n|-\n! width=\"50\"|<small>[[Top Country Albums|US Country]]</small>\n! width=\"50\"|<small>[[Billboard 200|US]]</small>\n! width=\"50\"|<small>[[Billboard charts#Albums|US Jazz]]</small>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|1981\n| ''It's Now or Never''\n| align=\"center\"|8\n| align=\"center\"|37\n| align=\"center\"|\u2014\n| rowspan=\"4\"|Scotti Brothers\n|-\n| ''White Christmas''\n| align=\"center\"|39\n| align=\"